1
00:00:08,179 --> 00:00:11,400
새벽 네 시 모니터 하나 켜놓고
At four in the morning, with one monitor turned on,

2
00:00:11,400 --> 00:00:15,000
줄줄이 코드를 써 내려가
I write down lines and lines of code.

3
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:18,519
에러 백 개쯤 지우고 나면
After deleting about a hundred errors,

4
00:00:18,519 --> 00:00:21,879
캐릭터 하나가 눈을 떠
A character opens its eyes.

5
00:00:21,879 --> 00:00:29,530
아무도 모르는 이 작은 세계
This small world that no one knows,

6
00:00:29,530 --> 00:00:33,090
내 손끝에서 태어나는 중
Is being born at my fingertips.

7
00:00:33,090 --> 00:00:37,969
픽셀 속의 꿈을 만들어가
Creating dreams within the pixels,

8
00:00:37,969 --> 00:00:41,530
한 칸 한 칸 점프해 올라가
Jumping up, one step at a time,

9
00:00:41,530 --> 00:00:44,810
버그투성이 밤을 건너서
Crossing through bug-ridden nights,

10
00:00:44,810 --> 00:01:07,170
나만의 게임이 시작돼
My very own game begins.

11
00:01:07,250 --> 00:01:08,969
스프라이트 하나 그려 넣으면
When I draw in a single sprite,

12
00:01:08,969 --> 00:01:12,489
작은 세상이 움직이잖아
The small world starts to move.

13
00:01:12,489 --> 00:01:16,209
혼자서 다 해야 하는 밤이
The nights when I have to do everything alone

14
00:01:16,209 --> 00:01:19,310
오히려 나를 웃게 만들어
Rather make me smile.

15
00:01:19,310 --> 00:01:24,489
완성 버튼을 누르는 그날
The day I press the complete button,

16
00:01:27,269 --> 00:01:31,150
온 세상이 플레이하게 될 거야
The whole world will play it.

17
00:01:31,150 --> 00:01:36,290
픽셀 속의 꿈을 만들어가
Creating dreams within the pixels,

18
00:01:36,290 --> 00:01:40,069
한 칸 한 칸 점프해 올라가
Jumping up, one step at a time,

19
00:01:40,069 --> 00:01:43,129
버그투성이 밤을 건너서
Crossing through bug-ridden nights,

20
00:01:43,129 --> 00:02:11,569
나만의 게임이 시작돼
My very own game begins.

21
00:02:11,569 --> 00:02:13,990
픽셀 속의 꿈을 만들어가
Creating dreams within the pixels,

22
00:02:13,990 --> 00:02:17,349
한 칸 한 칸 점프해 올라가
Jumping up, one step at a time,

23
00:02:17,349 --> 00:02:20,930
언젠가 누군가 플레이할 때
Someday, when someone plays it,

24
00:02:20,930 --> 00:02:25,770
이 밤의 코드가 빛이 돼
The code of this night will become light.

